&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Education/Experience&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;BA/BS in marketing, business administration, communications, or related field.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
