&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHO WE ARE&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;On Board Experiential (OBE) is an award winning, full service, experience-led agency that creates meaningful brand experiences worldwide, with office locations in London, San Francisco, Los Angeles and NYC.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We help brands to cut through the noise, capture consumer attention and leave lasting impressions that live beyond the shareable, streamable, screamable moment.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are specialists in creating extraordinary brand events – immersive, engaging and unrivalled.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The London office is the most recent to open its doors in the OBE family, making us the new kids on the block, but backed by years of experiential experience. Boasting a heavy hitting portfolio of incredibly active brands and a range of well-established partners, we’re well set for an exciting future.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking to add to our portfolio of Freelance Event Producers to work across our most high-profile accounts, as we continue to define experiential marketing and help achieve targeted growth.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We work with brands that care. Brands that value meaningful relationships. Brands that are prepared to challenge what’s gone before. Brands that aren’t prepared to settle for OK. Brands that want the competitive advantage. Brands that act.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are OBE and we’re a team of experiential playmakers.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;THE ROLE&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A Freelance Event Producer is responsible for creating heightened moments of in-person engagement with impact. This role manages all the elements that come together to create the live delivery aspect of our campaigns in relation to our client work.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Key responsibilities of the role could focus on:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Operational planning&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Operational execution&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Creative thinking&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Freelance Event Producer could work across all aspects of experiential delivery for one or more of our exciting portfolio of clients; a roster which currently includes Nike, NFL, New York Jets, JPMorganChase, OpenAI and Sky Bet. An excellent multi-tasker and someone who can manage multiple projects; from large scale campaigns to smaller bespoke activations in a wide range of settings.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A Freelance Event Producer is responsible for all live experience touch points and will ensure that OBE London provide a service for ‘in real life’ moments that are best in class and deliver to our client’s needs.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;On a day-to-day basis, the Freelance Event Producer will work collaboratively and creatively with colleagues and the client in order to deliver high quality campaigns. Fresh thinking is part of our DNA, to bring disruptive and innovative ideas to all our campaigns. The Freelance Event Producer plays a fundamental role in the process of creative solutions for our client work. This individual is to have / gain quickly the highest level of understanding of their clients’ needs, their brand and the space they operate in.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;RESPONSIBILITIES&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Freelance Event Producer role is varied, and you are responsible for:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;u&gt;Experiential Delivery&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Have a fresh thinking mindset and one that pushes boundaries&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Have a passion / obsession for our client’s consumers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide innovative and creative solutions in the design and delivery phase of campaigns&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Implement the executional plan in line with client requirements&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure consistency of delivery across live experiences&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li

